      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im having a really hard time sleeping lately. like i can barely stay asleep for more than a couple hours. i already take melatonin every night but it doesnt really do much anymore. my doctor gave me some zolpidem (ambien) to help but i was wondering if its okay if i take the melatonin and the ambien at the same time? just to make sure i actually stay asleep through the night? would that be safe to do?",
