      "content": "thanks for the info. i was a bit worried though about being too groggy the next day if i take both. should i maybe take a slightly higher dose of the melatonin than usual since i'm adding the ambien in? like if i usually take 3mg maybe i should try 10mg so it really kicks in? or is there a trick to it so i dont feel like a zombie in the morning?",
